## Public Directory

```
public/
├── 404.html                   # Not found page
├── 422.html                   # Unprocessable entity page
├── 500.html                   # Server error page
├── robots.txt                 # Search engine instructions
└── favicon.ico                # Favicon
```

**Rules:**
- Only static files that don't need processing
- Error pages are plain HTML
